@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qphbmn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.32 + v1 + 0.42) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.96)) + 0.16)
    v0 = (0.15 * ((tmp + 0.98 * v0 + 0.94) * 0.09))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
